name: VIDEO: County Welcomes New Hires at Job Fair
description: The County of San Diego is hiring. At an all-day job fair at the Southeastern Live Well Center, applicants had the opportunity to apply for positions in multiple departments and at varying levels. Same day interviews were scheduled and some lucky candidates left with a new County job. Get more information about job positions at the County.
